        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Shan Cai, an 18-year-old girl from a struggling family, is accepted into the country's most prestigious school, where she meets F4, an exclusive group of the wealthiest and most handsome boys—Dao Ming Si, Hua Ze Lei, Xi Men, and Mei Zuo. Despite Dao Ming Si's bullying, Shan Cai remains defiant and resilient. With Hua Ze Lei’s support, she endures the boys’ pranks and starts to gain their respect. As she uncovers theirtrue sides, her determination and the boys’ evolving feelings lead to friendship and eventual romance.",
